# Commit Author

**NEVER** use "Cursor", "Cursor Agent", "AI", or any automated agent as the author of commits, package metadata, or documentation.

- **Git commits**: Use the repository owner's identity. Author must be a human (e.g. Muyukani Ephraim Kizito).
- **Cargo.toml / package.json authors**: Use the project owner, never Cursor or AI.
- **AUTHORS / CONTRIBUTORS**: Do not list Cursor, AI assistants, or agents.

When making commits or suggesting author metadata, use the human repository owner only.
